# Override .gitignore for Cursor indexing/search.
# The .gitignore excludes **/reference/ and *.txt to keep copyrighted
# documents out of version control. We still want Cursor's tools
# (grep, semantic search) to be able to read the extracted text files.
#
# NOTE: ripgrep still respects .gitignore by default, so when using
# grep on reference .txt files, pass glob="*.txt" to force inclusion.
# The read_file tool always works regardless of ignore rules.
